  "prompt": "Which is the best app to make anonymous call online?",
  "response": "There are several apps that allow you to make anonymous calls online. Some popular options include:\n\n1. **Hushed**: This app provides you with a temporary phone number that you can use to make calls and send texts anonymously.\n\n2. **Burner**: Similar to Hushed, Burner allows you to create temporary phone numbers for anonymous communication.\n\n3. **SpoofCard**: This app enables you to change the caller ID that appears on the recipient's phone, effectively making your call anonymous.\n\n4. **Google Voice**: Although primarily used for forwarding calls and messages, Google Voice allows you to create an account with an anonymous number.\n\n5. **TextNow**: Besides messaging, TextNow offers the ability to make calls using a second number that can help maintain your privacy.\n\n6. **Phoner**: This app gives you the ability to create multiple phone numbers and make anonymous calls.\n\nKeep in mind the legal implications and terms of use when making anonymous calls, as misuse can lead to serious consequences. Always ensure that you're using such services ethically and within the boundaries of the law.",
